testsuite.name: dungeonmania.mvp.DoorsKeysTest

testcase.name: Test player can pick up a key and add to inventory
Test player cannot pickup two keys at the same time
Test player can use a key to open and walk through a door
Test player cannot walk through a closed door
Test doors remain open and the player can move through the door without a key
Test player cannot open a door with the wrong key
Test player can pick up a second key after using the first
